====Adjective====
{{en-adj}}

# {{not comparable}} Which is not [[closed]]; [[accessible]]; as, an open gate.
#:''Turn left after the second '''open''' door.''
# {{not comparable}} Actively conducting or prepared to [[conduct]] [[business]].
#:''Banks are not '''open''' on bank holidays.''
